						<div class="postbody">Yeah, I'm aware of severeal tools that can do it. I'm not terribly concerned about finding the minimum possible file size, it's just that the difference between any reasonable GIF optimizer (e.g. GIMP) and no optimizing at all (e.g. aseprite) can be pretty big.</div>

